Some help for you to get in and out dwm
=======================================

How to open another terminal emulator
-------------------------------------

Press Shift-Alt-ENTER


Tutorial about DWM
------------------

A tutorial is also available here:
http://dwm.suckless.org/tutorial


How to close dwm
----------------

To exit this Window Manager, please :
* press Shift-Alt-Q for QWERTY keyboard
* press Shift-Alt-A for AZERTY keyboard
* etc… (the key just at the right of tab)

Note: in rescue session, keys have been hard-coded for robustness against 
keyboard layouts that do not have direct access to numbers,
or have a no conventional HJKL placement.



Press ENTER to close this window and exit the session
